{
  "name": "RPlog_Swoop_Racing_on_Theseus",
  "title": "Swoop Racing on Theseus",
  "summary": "At the Titania Invitational of the Galactic Swoop League, Imperial pilot Danik Kreldin watches and races the deadly Grade 3 course aboard the Dark Wind, clearing its nebulas, comet rides, ion-cannon gauntlets and a mock Death Star superlaser run to seize the division lead. In the spectators' deck he is approached by Talia Andorn, a red-haired Noiri swooper who scents on him the trace of one of her own kind, Kao Ijuf, and grows suspicious about the woman's true origins. A later heat pits Danik's friend Reanus on the Starblade against his rival Daana Roon on the Turn of Fate, a brutal duel in which both racers take injuries and damage before Reanus narrowly edges ahead. Between races Danik trades flirtatious banter with Lady Athena, CEO of Dragons of Coruscant and organizer of the after-party, while Talia and her companion Mella keep circling back to question Danik about the mysterious Kao, the announcer's running commentary and the GSL leader board framing the day's spectacle.",
